Create Groups of Endpoints

Source: R/new_group.R
groups.Rd

Create Groups of Endpoints

Usage

new_group(
  member_names,
  group_name = NULL,
  quick_call = FALSE,
  offset = 0,
  limit = 10
)

pro_group(alias, ...)

Arguments

member_names

<chr> Alias representing the CMS data endpoint.

group_name

<chr> Name of the group.

quick_call

<lgl> call quick_() method on group if TRUE.

offset

<int> Offset for pagination.

limit

<int> Limit for pagination.

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

...

Additional arguments passed to the group constructor

Value

S7 class_group object.

Examples
